Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.68,0:01:47.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Depois que seu guia, Pekoms, desapareceu, Luffy e os outros deixaram a Ilha Cacao...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.85,0:01:51.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...e estão indo para Whole Cake Island,\N onde está Big Mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.42,0:01:54.34,Title,,0,0,170,,{\fad(1000,1000)}Yonkou, Charlotte Linlin
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.08,0:01:53.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,seguindo as instruções de Pudding.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.13,0:01:59.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Estou preocupado com o Pekoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.24,0:02:00.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos procurá-lo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.66,0:02:03.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Agradeço, mas isso não será fácil.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.64,0:02:05.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele é durão, não precisa se preocupar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.14,0:02:07.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim, mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.48,0:02:11.19,Main,,0,0,0,,De qualquer forma, precisamos chegar a Whole Cake Island...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.19,0:02:13.07,Main,,0,0,0,,...sem sermos descobertos pelo inimigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.07,0:02:15.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei, quanto falta?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.82,0:02:22.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Ainda não se passou muito tempo \Ndesde que deixamos a Ilha Cacao.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.50,0:02:28.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei, ilha à vista!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.63,0:02:32.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Legal, que doce nos espera?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:34.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Pelo cheiro,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:36.05,Main,,0,0,0,,deve ser algo doce!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.05,0:02:39.38,Main,,0,0,0,,O próximo deve ser uma \Ncidade feita de geleia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.38,0:02:41.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Geleia?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.38,0:02:41.08,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Geleia?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.08,0:02:42.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas não vamos desembarcar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.69,0:02:44.02,Main,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.69,0:02:44.02,Secondary,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.02,0:02:46.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Olhem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.10,0:02:47.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Quando virmos a Ilha Jam,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.82,0:02:51.35,Main,,0,0,0,,vamos seguir para a segunda agulha \Ndo Log Pose em vez de nos aproximarmos.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.35,0:02:53.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Mesmo que seja doce?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.37,0:02:54.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.72,0:02:58.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Não vamos desembarcar mesmo sendo doce?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.49,0:02:59.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos ver...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.40,0:03:01.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Por ali.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.96,0:03:03.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Legal!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.87,0:03:06.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy, a estibordo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.71,0:03:08.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Às três horas!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.26,0:03:12.43,NDTBoard,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\1a&H80&\fad(300,0)\t(0,300,\fscx570)\move(133,65,133,-57,2210,2710)}Mola
