Dialogue: 2,0:03:08.26,0:03:12.43,NDTHat,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,2210,2710)}Chibukai
Dialogue: 3,0:03:08.26,0:03:12.43,NDTHat2,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,2210,2710)}Fansub!
Dialogue: 4,0:03:08.26,0:03:12.43,NDTText,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\alpha&HFF&\t(300,600,\alpha&H00&)\move(650,35,650,-81,2210,2710)}Sanji se traduz como três horas. {sign not present in SC sub, translated it myself}
Comment: 0,0:03:08.26,0:03:12.43,Note,,0,0,0,,Sanji translates to Three O' Clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.26,0:03:10.00,Main,,0,0,0,,É verdade, Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:10.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Carrot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.97,0:03:12.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Para o Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.43,0:03:14.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas é doce!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.43,0:03:14.05,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Mas é doce!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.45,0:03:16.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos atrás do Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:18.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Todos a estibordo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.27,0:03:19.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Você está virando demais!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:21.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Você é muito ruim no leme, Luffy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.89,0:03:23.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Você também, Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.77,0:03:26.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas é doce...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.77,0:03:26.57,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Mas é doce...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.57,0:03:30.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele disse que, ao irmos para a próxima ilha \Nsem nos aproximarmos da outra ilha,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.94,0:03:34.48,Main,,0,0,0,,podemos evitar os sistemas de vigilância.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.48,0:03:38.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Entendi, então é assim que se lê o mapa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.41,0:03:39.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Você consegue?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.70,0:03:40.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Conte comigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.87,0:03:44.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy-san, eu vou cuidar disso agora.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.13,0:03:45.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.16,0:03:48.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Certo, pessoal, vou cozinhar algo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.12,0:03:48.81,Main,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.12,0:03:48.81,Secondary,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.34,0:03:51.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu preciso cozinhar!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.21,0:03:52.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Por favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.17,0:03:54.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy, espera um pouco!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:55.60,Main,,0,0,0,,O que foi, Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.60,0:03:56.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Vou cozinhar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.54,0:03:57.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Não!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.78,0:03:59.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Não vou errar desta vez!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.92,0:04:01.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu vou fazer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:04.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Não entre na cozinha de novo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.39,0:04:06.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Não vou te pagar!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.31,0:04:07.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Não preciso disso!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.48,0:04:09.02,Main,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.48,0:04:09.02,Secondary,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.86,0:04:13.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos trocar, Pedro?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:15.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Quero trabalhar!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.82,0:04:16.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Entendi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.35,0:04:21.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos ver...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.36,0:04:24.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:27.00,Main,,0,0,0,,O mar está da cor das uvas!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.50,0:04:29.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Cor das uvas?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.33,0:04:32.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Tem uma ilha por onde flui suco por perto.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.12,0:04:33.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Não é perigoso.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.30,0:04:34.31,Main,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.31,0:04:36.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Isso é suco?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.23,0:04:38.17,Main,,0,0,0,,É um paraíso sem fim!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.86,0:04:41.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Pedro, como você sabe tanto sobre este lugar?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:47.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Já vim aqui antes. {removed Sì, since its not part of the line in pace}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.14,0:04:48.18,Main,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.14,0:04:48.18,Secondary,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.49,0:04:56.38,Main,,0,0,0,,É enorme!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:04:59.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Legal!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.22,0:05:00.45,Main,,0,0,0,,É grande!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.33,0:05:03.11,Main,,0,0,0,,É um centopeia gigante.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.11,0:05:05.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Eles habitam esses mares.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:09.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Centopeia gigante, vá embora!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.81,0:05:11.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele vai nos comer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:13.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy, é a sua vez!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.63,0:05:14.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Beleza!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.84,0:05:20.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu também vou dar o meu melhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:28.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Lá vem ele!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:28.79,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Lá vem ele!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.79,0:05:31.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Gomu Gomu no...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.72,0:05:34.03,Main,,0,0,0,,...Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.81,0:05:51.70,Principio,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Enquanto isso, em Whole Cake Island...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.12,0:05:54.62,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,545)\fad(542,0)}WHOLE CAKE ISLAND
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.70,0:05:54.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Croquembouche!{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.82,0:05:59.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.82,0:05:59.14,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.14,0:06:01.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Pare, mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.14,0:06:01.14,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Pare, mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:09.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Mama, mama, pare!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:10.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Afaste-se!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:13.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Croquembouche!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:15.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, não!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:18.04,Main,,0,0,0,,É a doença da mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.04,0:06:20.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Rápido-bon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.11,0:06:22.72,Main,,0,0,0,,O que ela quer dessa vez-soir?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.72,0:06:23.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Ela quer...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.75,0:06:26.82,Main,,0,0,0,,...croquembouche!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.82,0:06:28.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Croquembouche?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.84,0:06:32.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Aquele doce decorado composto \Nde profiteroles empilhados?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.54,0:06:35.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Que pedido...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.09,0:06:36.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.14,0:06:37.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Não, esperem!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:39.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Se não me engano,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.84,0:06:44.00,Main,,0,0,0,,havia um grupo de profiteroles que vieram de turistas no hotel da cidade-je t'aime!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:46.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Eles foram embora de manhã.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.01,0:06:48.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Não temos outra opção a não ser preparar?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.02,0:06:49.30,Main,,0,0,0,,O que o chef disse?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.30,0:06:51.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Quero focar na massa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.28,0:06:54.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Conseguem amêndoas para nós?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:56.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Vou entrar em contato com o Ministro das Frutas Secas!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:59.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Mama está indo para Sweet City!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:01.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Ela está vindo para cá?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.62,0:07:03.05,Main,,0,0,0,,É a capital!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.05,0:07:04.10,Main,,0,0,0,,O castelo dela está aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.10,0:07:06.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Não conseguimos conversar com ela!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.22,0:07:08.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Ela perdeu toda a razão por causa do seu ataque!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.02,0:07:14.11,Main,,0,0,0,,As baixas continuam aumentando!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.11,0:07:17.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Ordenem a evacuação de Sweet City!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.44,0:07:21.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Só o croquembouche pode parar a mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.46,0:07:22.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Por aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:23.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Evacuem rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.51,0:07:24.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:28.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Mama, pare, por favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:31.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Mama, vamos parar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:31.13,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Mama, vamos parar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.59,0:07:36.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Me tragam croquembouche!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:41.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Mama entrou em Sweet City!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.20,0:07:42.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Ela entrou em Sweet City!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.85,0:07:45.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, finalmente chegou...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:49.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Os desejos da mama são perigosos-bon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.47,0:07:52.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Porque seus ataques são repentinos.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.24,0:07:58.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Ela continuará destruindo até \Ncomer o que deseja!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:08:02.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Seja como for, evacuem os civis!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.04,0:08:03.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Fujam!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:03.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.93,0:08:05.88,Main,,0,0,0,,É uma birra da Big Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:07.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Pare!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.28,0:08:08.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Nessa cidade?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.64,0:08:16.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Mama, mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.57,0:08:18.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Não nesta cidade!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.47,0:08:20.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Ela pode até destruir o castelo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.88,0:08:21.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Impossível.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.91,0:08:23.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Ela não nos escuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.15,0:08:37.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Croquembouche!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.54,0:08:45.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Croquembouche!{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.96,0:08:54.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Não é!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.76,0:08:57.76,Main,,0,0,0,,E-Ela está vindo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:15.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Não é esse sabor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.72,0:09:18.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Vocês também não são!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.54,0:09:21.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Nada disso é!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:27.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Croquembouche!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:30.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Obrigado!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.89,0:09:34.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, é Moscato-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:37.98,Main,,0,0,0,,O décimo sexto filho da \Nfamília Charlotte e o Ministro do Sorvete!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.98,0:09:39.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Se é um membro da família,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.57,0:09:41.50,Main,,0,0,0,,com certeza poderá fazer algo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.51,0:09:44.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Moscato falando!{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.02,0:09:46.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Como está o croquembouche?!{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.50,0:09:46.02,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,480)\fad(534,0)}DÉCIMO SEXTO FILHO DA FAMÍLIA CHARLOTTE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.50,0:09:46.02,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,710)\fad(534,0)}CHARLOTTE MOSCATO - MINISTRO DO SORVETE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.02,0:09:50.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Dizem que levará mais meia hora\N para ficar pronto-bon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.58,0:09:53.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Não vamos conseguir a tempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.28,0:09:55.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Não podemos deixar que ela destrua o castelo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.70,0:10:01.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Não é!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:03.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:05.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Pare, por favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.44,0:10:07.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Quem é?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.29,0:10:12.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.37,0:10:13.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Sou eu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.57,0:10:14.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Moscato!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.99,0:10:23.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Onde está meu croquembouche?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.54,0:10:26.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Croquembouche...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:28.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Croquembouche!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.98,0:10:31.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Em trinta minutos estará pronto!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.60,0:10:34.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Agora mesmo os chefs estão\N preparando com urgência!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.65,0:10:36.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Pare, irmão Mos!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.74,0:10:38.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Parar ela é impossível!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.70,0:10:41.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Está me dizendo para deixá-la destruir a capital?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.55,0:10:45.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Saia da frente!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.71,0:10:52.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Não me reconhece, mama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:06.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Doce...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:07.60,Main,,0,0,0,,...ou...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.61,0:11:11.35,Main,,0,0,0,,...vida!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.94,0:11:20.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Doce ou vida...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.20,0:11:22.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Vida ou doce!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.36,0:11:24.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Não brinque, mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.71,0:11:26.24,Main,,0,0,0,,É o seu próprio filho!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:28.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Mama, pare!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.30,0:11:31.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Temos creme fresco-fa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.55,0:11:34.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Ainda não está cozido, mas pare, mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.94,0:11:37.55,Main,,0,0,0,,O-O doce ainda não chegou!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.55,0:11:40.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Vou comer os doces...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.62,0:11:43.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Não atrapalhe!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:12:00.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.19,0:12:02.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Moscato, acalme-se!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.99,0:12:06.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Não-fa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.60,0:12:08.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Qualquer sinal de medo e sua expectativa de vida será reduzida!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.82,0:12:19.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Me perdoe, mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.12,0:12:21.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Não vou mais te deter!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.22,0:12:22.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Por favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:24.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Não me mate!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.01,0:12:44.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Quarenta anos...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.04,0:12:52.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Irmão!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.02,0:12:56.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Moscato-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.02,0:12:56.03,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Moscato-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.03,0:12:57.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Ela matou...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.92,0:13:02.32,Main,,0,0,0,,...seu próprio filho!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.42,0:13:09.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Croquembouche!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.67,0:13:11.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Fujam!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.24,0:13:13.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Ninguém pode detê-la agora!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.48,0:13:21.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Que situação terrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.16,0:13:31.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Alguém está vindo pelo rio de suco!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.08,0:13:32.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Esse é...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.40,0:13:33.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele é...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.33,0:13:34.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Não há dúvida!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:37.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Afaste-se!{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.04,0:13:40.54,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,480)\fad(534,0)}CAPITÃO DOS PIRATAS DO SOL
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.04,0:13:40.54,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,710)\fad(534,0)}JINBE - EX-SHICHIBUKAI
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.83,0:13:40.54,Main,,0,0,0,,É o Chefe Jinbe!{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.13,0:13:43.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Socorro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.21,0:13:45.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos ser comidos!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.18,0:13:48.85,Main,,0,0,0,,E ele trouxe um croquembouche!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.85,0:13:52.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele capturou os profiteroles \Nque estavam no hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.64,0:13:54.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Estão cobertos de caramelo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:13:57.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Será que foi o Ministro dos Doces?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.56,0:14:04.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Aqui está!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:07.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Não se intrometa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:11.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Aceite!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.68,0:14:38.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Delicioso!{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.01,0:14:41.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele conseguiu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.46,0:14:43.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Mama superou seu ataque de fúria!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.98,0:14:47.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.81,0:14:52.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Se estiver delicioso, é isso que importa...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.13,0:14:55.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Obrigado, Chefe Jinbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.95,0:14:58.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Contatem os chefes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.62,0:15:00.08,Main,,0,0,0,,A crise acabou!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.08,0:15:02.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Convoquem todos os ministros!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.44,0:15:06.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Reparem a capital o mais rápido possível-bon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.80,0:15:14.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas é o Jinbe, meu leal guerreiro dos mares!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:19.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Bom trabalho trazendo o Poneglyph no outro dia.{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.68,0:15:23.36,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,480)\fad(534,0)}YONKOU - CAPITÃ DOS PIRATAS DE BIG MOM
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.68,0:15:23.36,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,710)\fad(534,0)}CHARLOTTE LINLIN - RAINHA DE TOTTO LAND
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.06,0:15:21.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Embora eu não consiga lê-lo.{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.86,0:15:29.51,Main,,0,0,0,,O que está acontecendo hoje?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.51,0:15:31.82,Main,,0,0,0,,O que estamos fazendo aqui?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.82,0:15:33.28,Main,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:36.33,Main,,0,0,0,,A cidade está mais melhor do que nunca.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.33,0:15:38.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Você fez isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.58,0:15:44.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Não, acabei de chegar, não sei o que aconteceu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.00,0:15:46.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.42,0:15:48.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Hoje eu vim...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.22,0:15:54.72,Main,,0,0,0,,...para falar de algo importante com você.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.89,0:16:04.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Você não vai deixar minha tripulação, vai?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:10.32,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,545)\fad(579,500)}HÁ ALGUMAS HORAS
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.04,0:16:17.41,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha Luffy é o homem\N que um dia mudará o mundo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.00,0:16:21.97,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Ele ainda é jovem, mas quem se \Ntornará o rei dos mares...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.97,0:16:24.71,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,...não será nenhum Yonkou!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.22,0:16:29.34,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Estou convencido de que será Chapéu de Palha Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.98,0:16:33.88,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Eu...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.97,0:16:38.31,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,...quero ajudá-lo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.32,0:16:46.70,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Eu sou {\alpha&HFF&}fraco!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.70,0:16:48.86,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Eu sou fraco!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.86,0:16:50.80,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Eu quero...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:54.50,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Eu quero embarcar no navio dele...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.50,0:16:57.82,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,...e dedicar minha vida a ele!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.82,0:17:04.46,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,No final, isso também contribuirá \Npara dar verdadeira liberdade aos homens-peixe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.71,0:17:13.47,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,445)\fad(579,500)}PRIMEIRO OFICIAL DOS PIRATAS DO SOL
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.71,0:17:13.47,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,710)\fad(579,500)}ALADDIN, SEREIA DE BROTULA
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.26,0:17:14.30,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Durante esses dois anos, você nos contou \Nmuito sobre Luffy-kun.{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:19.93,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Se você o admira tanto, acho que \Né isso que você deveria fazer.{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.86,0:17:22.68,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,S-Sério?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.28,0:17:25.64,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Eu falei tanto sobre ele?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.25,0:17:30.65,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Vá, Jinbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.59,0:17:35.32,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Eu tenho sua aprovação?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:40.74,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Ninguém aqui pode te dizer \Nnada sobre isso, capitão!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:46.60,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Sim, você era um soldado do Exército de Netuno e depois se tornou um pirata...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.60,0:17:51.67,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,...para lutar conosco, \Nescravos libertados de Mary Geoise!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.67,0:17:57.04,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Você também se tornou um Shichibukai \Npara melhorar a posição dos homens-peixe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.04,0:18:01.57,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,E se juntou aos Piratas de Big Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.57,0:18:07.98,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,...para nos proteger e ao Reino Ryugu usando o nome dela!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.98,0:18:13.71,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Todas as decisões da sua vida \Nforam tomadas pensando nos outros!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.28,0:18:18.21,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Já é suficiente, Jinbe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.83,0:18:22.08,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Isso mesmo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.08,0:18:24.29,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Seja livre, Jinbe-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.29,0:18:26.22,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Vá, Jinbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.22,0:18:28.38,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Isso, Capitão Jinbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.38,0:18:30.77,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Nós vamos nos virar sem você!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.77,0:18:32.21,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Não nos subestime!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:36.09,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Agora viva por você, por favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.15,0:18:53.77,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Pessoal...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.77,0:18:55.37,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Obrigado!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.85,0:19:12.00,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Mas acho que Big Mom não vai \Ndeixar o capitão ir tão facilmente...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.00,0:19:17.61,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Se ela ficar brava conosco, \Nnão teremos outra escolha a não ser fugir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.61,0:19:20.34,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Mas e o Aladdin-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.12,0:19:25.87,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Ele se casou com a senhorita Praline e se tornou parte da família de Big Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.87,0:19:27.97,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Ora, ora...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.66,0:19:32.81,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Estão preocupados comigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:34.36,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Oh, senhorita!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.86,0:19:39.24,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,445)\fad(369,0)}FILHA VIGÉSIMA NONA DA FAMÍLIA CHARLOTTE
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.86,0:19:39.24,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,710)\fad(369,0)}CHARLOTTE PRALINE (MEIA-SEREIA DE TUBARÃO-MARTELO)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:42.45,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Falando pelas minhas costas?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.45,0:19:44.99,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Quer dizer que ela nos ouviu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.99,0:19:46.75,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Como você pode ser tão frio?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.75,0:19:48.98,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Você está escondendo coisas de mim?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.98,0:19:50.15,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Aladdin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.15,0:19:56.26,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Não me diga que você está pensando em me deixar \Nse a mama ficar brava com vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.26,0:19:58.63,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Não, é claro que eu consultaria você primeiro...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.63,0:20:01.09,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Você não precisa me consultar!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.09,0:20:04.60,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Eu escolheria você em vez da mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.60,0:20:07.14,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Se algo acontecer, leve-me com você!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.14,0:20:09.06,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Oh, que ardente!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.14,0:20:09.06,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Oh, que ardente!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.13,0:20:13.08,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Desculpe, Wadatsumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.08,0:20:16.09,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Eu te trouxe aqui com muita \Nurgência, mas você já ouviu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.09,0:20:18.20,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Não tem problema!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.20,0:20:21.60,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Eu me divirto muito estando com vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.51,0:20:29.46,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Bem, Praline, você acha que a mama vai me perdoar?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.46,0:20:31.50,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Digo, a nós.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:38.87,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Bem, não é a primeira vez que isso acontece, mas \Ntodos aqueles que quiseram deixar a tripulação...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.87,0:20:40.71,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,...morreram.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.10,0:20:46.06,OPLetreros,,1000,0,240,,{\fad(250,250)\pos(1130,405)}O PRESENTE:\N WHOLE CAKE ISLAND {sign not present in SC, translated it myself}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.34,0:20:50.47,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(642,483)}SWEET CITY\N CAPITAL DE WHOLE CAKE ISLAND{\fad(650,0)} {sign not present in SC, translated it myself}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.07,0:21:07.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Moscato-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.32,0:21:10.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Moscato-sama morreu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.66,0:21:13.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Não morra, Moscato-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.62,0:21:16.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Moscato-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.34,0:21:25.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Finalmente chegaram.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.53,0:21:34.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Levem-no imediatamente.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.00,0:21:34.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.60,0:21:36.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Saia da frente.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.12,0:21:48.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Escutem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.32,0:21:50.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Não deixem um segundo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.65,0:21:52.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Entendido?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.21,0:22:03.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Moscato-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.67,0:22:11.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei, o chefe Jinbe também vai ser \Nassassinado, Montd'Or-sama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.28,0:22:12.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Não sei!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.98,0:22:16.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Quando a mamãe fica brava, até \Nseus próprios filhos podem acabar assim.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.92,0:22:18.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Isso é um fato!
Comment: 0,0:22:22.30,0:22:28.58,Captions,,10,0,420,,{\fad(250,250)}Sweet City\NWhole Cake Chateau
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.30,0:22:28.58,OPLetreros,,10,0,420,,{\pos(640,295)\fad(250,250)}SWEET CITY\N PASTEL CHATEAU {sign not present in SC, used translation from the spanish manga for PASTEL CHATEAU}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.68,0:22:32.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Então você está indo embora, Jinbe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.56,0:22:37.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Por quê, chefe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.14,0:22:38.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Não vá, chefe!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.45,0:22:39.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Por que você está indo embora?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.57,0:22:40.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Cale-se!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.88,0:22:50.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Não peçam razões para alguém que quer ir embora!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.45,0:22:51.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Isso é patético!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.60,0:22:54.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Não importa!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.46,0:23:02.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Se você é um pirata, deve viver como quiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.01,0:23:04.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Sou delicioso?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.28,0:23:05.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Diga se sou delicio...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.22,0:23:10.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.14,0:23:13.82,Main,,0,0,0,,...é uma vergonha para um chefe...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.82,0:23:15.90,Main,,0,0,0,,...ir contra seu voto de lealdade.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.88,0:23:23.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Jinbe, isso significa que \Nvou perder você, uma grande força militar.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.11,0:23:24.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim, mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.92,0:23:27.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Nada de "mas"!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.51,0:23:30.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Você tem que perder algo também!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.49,0:23:33.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Você tem que pagar a dívida!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.63,0:23:41.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Traga-me a roleta!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.50,0:23:42.81,Main,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.50,0:23:42.81,Secondary,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.60,0:24:00.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos, gire-a.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.00,0:24:11.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos ver o que você vai perder!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.18,0:24:23.27,Principio,,0,0,0,,Enquanto isso, Luffy e os outros estavam \Nno mar dominado por Big Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.92,0:24:27.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Está doce!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.89,0:24:31.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Seja como for, não se move.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.34,0:24:32.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Nao...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.63,0:24:35.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Bom, vamos ficar aqui para dormir!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.43,0:24:36.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Nao!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.54,0:24:39.29,Main,,0,0,0,,E se as formigas nos atacarem de novo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.29,0:24:43.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Quando o sol nascer, \Nvai se tornar liquido de novo.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.16,0:24:46.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas durante a noite o mar congela.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.44,0:24:49.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Devia ter falado isso antes!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.96,0:24:55.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos derreter e sair logo \Ndeste mar de xarope!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.11,0:24:55.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.84,0:24:57.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Um, dois!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.95,0:25:01.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Só colocamos as formigas para dormir!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.60,0:25:04.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos ter problemas quando elas acordarem.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.15,0:25:05.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Isso mesmo.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.77,0:25:12.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Há muito tempo essas formigas \Nmarinhas devoraram meu barco.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.55,0:25:13.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Que medo!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.53,0:25:15.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Há muito tempo?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.37,0:25:17.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Há muito tempo?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.66,0:25:22.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Pedro e Pekoms estiveram\N na mesma tripulação pirata.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.15,0:25:23.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.02,0:25:23.91,Main,,0,0,0,,De verdade?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.20,0:25:27.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Nao sabia nada sobre o mundo.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.70,0:25:31.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Queria ser um explorador, mas acabei com uma recompensa na minha cabeça.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.96,0:25:34.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Só fiquei com Pekoms e \Nos outros até a metade do caminho.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.68,0:25:39.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Como se trata de vocês, vou contar.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.60,0:25:45.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Estive procurando Poneglyphs para\N ajudar o senhor Nekomamushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.19,0:25:53.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas minhas viagens terminaram quando \Nentrei no território de Big Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.22,0:25:57.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.45,0:26:00.36,Main,,0,0,0,,...perdi aqui.{\fad(0,1056)}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.03,0:26:09.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,516)}Nao é algo de que eu fale muito.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.96,0:26:12.34,Main,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,762)}Entao foi assim...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.30,0:26:23.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Apesar dessas más \Nlembranças, decidiu voltar?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.77,0:26:29.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Se minha experiência for útil \Npara salvar Sanji, ficarei satisfeito.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.61,0:26:32.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Além disso,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.61,0:26:36.48,Main,,0,0,0,,não posso dizer que vir \Ncom vocês foi em vão.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.54,0:26:43.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Na árvore baleia, nossos reis \Nmostraram a vocês o Road Poneglyph.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.20,0:26:44.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.74,0:26:47.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Fiquei surpreso.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.79,0:26:49.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Apesar de nos terem salvado,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.64,0:26:53.17,Main,,0,0,0,,não mostraram para \Nninguém além dos Kouzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.17,0:26:56.13,Main,,0,0,0,,...por vinte e seis anos...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.13,0:26:59.84,Main,,0,0,0,,...desde que mostraram \Naos piratas de Gol D. Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.56,0:27:01.93,Main,,0,0,0,,O Rei dos Piratas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.36,0:27:07.45,Main,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1032)}Depois, Roger chegou a Laugh Tale e\N foi chamado de Rei dos Piratas.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.64,0:27:16.11,Main,,0,0,0,,O Duque Inuarashi e o senhor Nekomamushi se lembraram deles quando viram vocês.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.61,0:27:23.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Eles acham que vocês\N precisarão dos Road Poneglyphs.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.99,0:27:27.70,Main,,0,0,0,,O que farão depois de derrotar Kaidou?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.70,0:27:30.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Nao há motivos para pensar \Nem algo que esta tão longe...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.79,0:27:34.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Depois você precisará do \NRoad Poneglyph que Big Mom possui!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.81,0:27:39.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Nesse caso, esta é a \Nmelhor oportunidade que temos!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.48,0:27:42.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Agora que entramos \Ntanto em seu território,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.55,0:27:48.14,Main,,0,0,0,,além de resgatar Sanji, devemos \Nroubar o Road Poneglyph de Big Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.39,0:27:51.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.22,0:27:53.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas isso...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.82,0:27:57.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Nao só Sanji, mas também o Road Poneglyph?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.37,0:28:05.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Bem, Robin também me pediu,\N mas primeiro quero salvar Sanji...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.42,0:28:07.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu sei.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.16,0:28:10.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu vou conseguir o Road Poneglyph.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.42,0:28:11.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Vocês cuidem de Sanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.89,0:28:12.87,Main,,0,0,0,,E-Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.63,0:28:18.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Me dão um pouco de tempo\N quando chegarmos à ilha?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.77,0:28:20.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Dessa vez eu vou roubar!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.47,0:28:24.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Não, se fizer por \Nnós, vamos com você!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.59,0:28:28.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Não, protejam bem Sanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.14,0:28:30.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Depois de resgatá-lo, nao será fácil.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.69,0:28:37.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Entendo.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.02,0:28:39.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Então, conto com você!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.36,0:28:41.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Beleza, está decidido!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.00,0:28:42.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Não decidam tão facilmente...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.52,0:28:49.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Será que Luffy-san nasceu sob essa estrela...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.78,0:28:51.86,Main,,0,0,0,,O que foi, Brook?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.86,0:28:53.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Nada.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.17,0:28:54.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu sinto o mesmo.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.87,0:28:56.11,Main,,0,0,0,,O que você sente?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.11,0:28:58.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Que estranho você é.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.81,0:29:13.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, as formigas acordaram!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.84,0:29:15.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Não!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.06,0:29:17.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Formiga, formiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.31,0:29:17.80,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Formiga, formiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.80,0:29:20.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Lá vem elas!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.15,0:29:22.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Protejam o Sunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.07,0:29:29.55,OPLetreros,,1000,0,310,,{\fad(250,250)\pos(1130,395)}NA MANHÃ SEGUINTE {sign not present in SC, used translation from spanish manga}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.28,0:29:36.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei, pessoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.30,0:29:37.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Acordem!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.03,0:29:42.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.80,0:29:43.97,Main,,0,0,0,,O que? O que?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.13,0:29:57.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Olhem, olhem!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.91,0:30:10.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Finalmente chegamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.28,0:30:21.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, é enorme!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.24,0:30:24.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Entao é nessa ilha que está a Yonkou!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.58,0:30:27.51,Main,,0,0,0,,É um bolo!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.59,0:30:34.51,Main,,0,0,0,,O bolo mais alto é \No castelo onde Big Mom vive!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.51,0:30:36.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Um castelo?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.15,0:30:38.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Nami-san, mantemos o curso?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.90,0:30:42.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim, ela disse que esse cabo\N é o único lugar sem guardas.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.85,0:30:44.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Entendi.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.57,0:30:47.10,Main,,0,0,0,,É o lugar que Pudding-san disse.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.10,0:30:50.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim, devemos agradecer a ela.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.81,0:30:54.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Se não fosse por ela, quem sabe\N se teríamos chegado até aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.53,0:30:56.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Verdade.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.41,0:31:00.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, tem alguém na costa!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.54,0:31:09.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.93,0:31:11.51,Main,,0,0,0,,É o Sanji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.51,0:31:13.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.17,0:31:15.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.17,0:31:17.30,Credits,,0,0,0,,Edicao de video:\N Feeso,\NGalaxy 9000\N\NTempos:\NHalee,\NSewil (Opening),\NUmim\N\NControle de qualidade:\NBastia,\NGalaxy 9000,\NGrug,\NMr. Luffy,\NPepperjack\N\NEdicao de audio:\N Halee\N\NLegendas:\NJuanTlgd\N\NRevisão:\NRAFAEL
